``````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
!define(   buildAlerts   )
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
<div class="alert-messages">
<div class="alert !ifdef(AlertType)(alert-\AlertType)">
\1
</div>
</div>
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


!comment(   Alert   )
``````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
DECRIPTION: Wraps the contents of the macro's parameter in Alert <div>s.
			Contents will be processed as markdown.
USAGE:

    !Alert
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    MARKDOWN BLOCK
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

``````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
!define(   Alert   )
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
!undefine(AlertType)
!buildAlerts(\1)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~



